<li><a href="http://www.adobe.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://www.adobe.com</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.reliablesoft.net/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">https://www.reliablesoft.net</a> ðŸ™‚</li>
